{"body": "Thanks!\r\n\r\nOne difference with the ActionView::Base solution is that you won't be able to activate and de-activate the prefixing on a per-controller basis. I don't actually have a use case for this but it seemed like a nice side effect.\r\n\r\nThat said, it's definitely more of a ActionView concern and it's probably better not to mix things up too much.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/4764570", "created_at": "2012-03-28T13:30:07Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/5625#issuecomment-4764570", "updated_at": "2012-03-28T13:30:07Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 5625, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nertzy/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nertzy/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nertzy/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/nertzy", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nertzy/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/nertzy", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nertzy/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/602f1b8ccf99dc47c43da83d53b4ffd5?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F7989edad14ebcd3adfacc7344dc6b739.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nertzy/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nertzy/received_events", "gravatar_id": "602f1b8ccf99dc47c43da83d53b4ffd5", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nertzy/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "nertzy", "type": "User", "id": 2488, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nertzy/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5238150ebd3543c15100dc8a"}, "id": 4764570, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/5625"}
